{"tid":1313032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開戰啦 呢場運動已經冇得逆轉","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:51:33.000Z","uid":302,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdb0be7f5d2680379e82697ecaa4ad1dc26cded","tid":1313032,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"政權一早已經與民為敵 呢場戰爭已經唔可以再停係和理非<br />\n無需要再去指班狗點樣點樣 因為根本投訴無number<br />\n有都好 監警會全部建制派唔會做野 特首身有屎唔會開調查委員會 所以警察當議員冇到 當記者為敵人 拉人亂咁拉 鍾意打你就打你 睇你唔順眼噴你胡椒又得 自己友打人就幾廿人元首級護送 幫你截埋的士開埋路 拉左既自己友 好似大波man咁做下樣轉頭放返你 <br />\n<br />\n既然政府唔聽訴求 唔回應 和理非非冇用 不合作運動比你圍返轉頭 ok 各位正式全面勇武 全部上齊gear <br />\n每次集會大家做定心理準備 要有作戰狀態 呢場運動已經全面升級 冇得逆轉"},{"pid":"c763e2a3e62c071d584eda4310b27e05728cf469","tid":1313032,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bNFY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bNFY6E.jpg&h=0e3ff068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJqqMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJqqMr.jpg&h=d5937562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUnCgTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUnCgTg.jpg&h=4d401a96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAgxru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAgxru.jpg&h=a97e178b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"6e